psalm.text:
[[Ps 136,1]]Give thanks to the LORD, for he is good, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,23]]Who remembered us in our abjection, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,24]]And freed us from our foes, 
for his mercy endures forever.

[[Ps 136,10]]Who smote the Egyptians in their first-born, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,11]]And brought out Israel from their midst, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,12]]With a mighty hand and an outstretched arm, 
for his mercy endures forever.

[[Ps 136,13]]Who split the Red Sea in twain, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,14]]And led Israel through its midst, 
for his mercy endures forever;
[[Ps 136,15]]But swept Pharaoh and his army into the Red Sea, 
for his mercy endures forever.
